autocmd FileType html inoremap ;th <th></th><Enter><++><Esc>k$4hi
autocmd FileType html inoremap ;td <td></td><Enter><++><Esc>k$4hi
autocmd FileType html inoremap ;fs <form<Space>action=""<Space>method=""><Enter><Enter><br><Enter><button<Space>type="submit">Submit</button><Enter></form><Enter><++><Esc>4ki
